snippet.title: MiG-29 Fulcrum (Novalogic, 1998) gameplay (PC Game, 1998)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for MiG-29 Fulcrum (Novalogic, 1998), PC game produced by NovaLogic in 1998 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/mig29-fulcrum-novalogic/15226/
MiG-29 Fulcrum is a solid simulation flight game with impressive graphics. You have different missions where you have to eliminate enemies by using the cannon and missiles.
Played through modern Windows machine.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:

Afterburner - https://youtu.be/EyADrOBV4EU
